              :EndIf
              rc←ExecuteTestFunction ref ps testNo testFns
              :If ' '=1↑0⍴rc   ⍝ Custom message?
                  :If (⊂rc)∊ListCustomMessages[;2]                      ⍝ Is it a valid custom message?
